    Number
    A number in text.
    NumberContextWriter
    Writes numbers and the context of tokens around them to files.
    The format is one line of up to 6 tokens in the sentence to the left of the number, one line making up all the tokens in the number, and one line of up to 6 tokens in the sentence to the right of the number.
